Sentencas: This study reports the successful preparation of single-phase perovslcite (Ba0.5Sr0.5)(0.8)La0.2Fe1-xMnxO3-delta (x = 0-0.2) by the citrate-EDTA cornplexing method.
Titulo: Conductivity and electrochemical performance of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)0.8La0.2Fe1-xMnxO3-δ cathode prepared by the citrate-EDTA complexing method

Sentencas: The crystal structure, thermal gravity analysis, coefficient of thermal expansion, electrical conductivity, and electrochemical performance of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)(0.8)La0.2Fe1-xMnxO3-delta were investigated to determine its suitability as a cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Conductivity and electrochemical performance of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)0.8La0.2Fe1-xMnxO3-δ cathode prepared by the citrate-EDTA complexing method

Sentencas: The lattice parameter a of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)(0.8)La0.2Fe1-xMnxO3-delta decreases as the amount of Mn doping increases.
Titulo: Conductivity and electrochemical performance of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)0.8La0.2Fe1-xMnxO3-δ cathode prepared by the citrate-EDTA complexing method

Sentencas: The coefficients of thermal expansion of the samples are in the range of 21.6-25.9 x 10(-6) K-1 and show an abnormal expansion at around 400 degrees C associated with the loss of lattice oxygen.
Titulo: Conductivity and electrochemical performance of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)0.8La0.2Fe1-xMnxO3-δ cathode prepared by the citrate-EDTA complexing method

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity of the (Ba0.5Sr0.5)(0.8)La0.2Fe1-xMnxO3-delta samples decreases as the amount of Mn-doping increases.
Titulo: Conductivity and electrochemical performance of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)0.8La0.2Fe1-xMnxO3-δ cathode prepared by the citrate-EDTA complexing method

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity of the samples reaches a maximum value at around 400 degrees C and then decreases as the temperature increases.
Titulo: Conductivity and electrochemical performance of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)0.8La0.2Fe1-xMnxO3-δ cathode prepared by the citrate-EDTA complexing method

Sentencas: The charge transfer resistance, diffusion resistance and total resistance of a (Ba0.5Sr0.5)(0.8)La0.2Fe0.8Mn0.15O3-delta-Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 composite cathode electrode at 800 degrees C are 0.11 Omega cm(2), 0.24 Omega cm(2) and 0.35 Omega cm(2), respectively.
Titulo: Conductivity and electrochemical performance of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)0.8La0.2Fe1-xMnxO3-δ cathode prepared by the citrate-EDTA complexing method
